        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2025-10-17T14:32:40Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stop Stealing Our Jobs Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits the President or the head of an executive agency from removing a federal employee from the civil service (e.g., as part of a reduction in force) during a lapse in discretionary appropriations (i.e., government shutdown) unless the employee is a political appointee.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
